00:56:01,447 --> 00:56:03,747
would only throw six
passes in the entire game.

814
00:56:03,749 --> 00:56:07,284
♪ There goes The Juice ♪
♪ There goes The Juice ♪

815
00:56:07,286 --> 00:56:09,620
The entire offense was O.J. Simpson.

816
00:56:09,622 --> 00:56:11,522
♪ There goes The Juice ♪

817
00:56:11,524 --> 00:56:13,290
♪ 30, 40... ♪

818
00:56:13,292 --> 00:56:16,460
Nobody actually thought
he was gonna go for 2,000.

819
00:56:16,462 --> 00:56:20,965
With only, uh, two games to go, he
was still 400 and a few yards short.

820
00:56:20,967 --> 00:56:22,399
Go, Juice!

821
00:56:22,401 --> 00:56:23,200
Come on, Juice!

822
00:56:25,438 --> 00:56:31,308
During the games, I never took
a minute off from the offense.

823
00:56:31,310 --> 00:56:34,778
♪ Do you want The Juice
to put a move on you? ♪

824
00:56:34,780 --> 00:56:36,747
I never made it to the bench.

